For windows:
	install cygwin (with mingw inside)
	install nullsoft NSIS in the default place
	inside cygwin go to picky root, run make
	inside win run make

For linux (debian-based):
	need debhelper, bison, gcc, make
	apt-get install build-essential bison
	go to picky root run make
	go to linux, run make


